N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 171.8 - Lists

State Regulations

Within 30 days of the completion of a 25-hour course, a
school must submit to the Department of State a list of the names and addresses
of each student who successfully completed the course. Notes
